    "name": "动物园模拟器",
    "steam_appid": 2129220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>翻修你的动物园！</strong></h2>在动物园模拟器游戏里，你的首要任务之一将是把动物园恢复如初。你必须要投入大量精力，为你未来要养的动物们清理不易注意到的小巷和被破坏的地方。做这些工作，你需要用到许多工具，诸如电焊机和高压水枪等。请记住 - 辛勤的工作后随之而来的将是一群快乐的游客！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/bd0c251654b18a0028758b64b593ee8c.poster.avif?t=1761218317\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/bd0c251654b18a0028758b64b593ee8c.webm?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/bd0c251654b18a0028758b64b593ee8c.mp4?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不同种类的动物</strong></h2>动物园里有动物生活才能叫动物园，是吧？在这款游戏里，你有权决定哪些动物可以生活在这片设施里。要知道，在动物园里生活着的动物越有意思，越会有更多的游客想去看它们，也就意味着你的生意会有更多的收入。坐下来看看电脑，从世界各地最奇特、最令人惊奇的动物中选择一些吧!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/5b8d6e2a79325983bf25295a0fdead4d.poster.avif?t=1761218317\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/5b8d6e2a79325983bf25295a0fdead4d.webm?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/5b8d6e2a79325983bf25295a0fdead4d.mp4?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为动物们奔走</strong></h2>你的动物园里会出现来自世界最遥远角落的动物，它们需要合适的生活条件 - 因此你必须为其提供好的巢穴、藏身处以及它们喜欢的植物。游戏中会出现多种不同的元素，你可以进行自由移动，定位及旋转，从而为动物们打造出独特的生活区域。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/15a2e377918e0633cb3f4c7a91c84ef5.poster.avif?t=1761218317\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/15a2e377918e0633cb3f4c7a91c84ef5.webm?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/15a2e377918e0633cb3f4c7a91c84ef5.mp4?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>时刻关心它们</strong></h2>在动物园模拟器游戏里，你还需要时刻注意动物们的健康状况，它们会以和平、健康及行动来回报你。按时给它们喂食、关心它们，并特别注意保证它们的安全 - 动物们喜欢咬他们的鼻子，只要有机会就会咬上一口! 正因为如此，动物才更有可能向游客展示自己，赢得他们的同情。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/f2210fce606d833c207fcf60055b9233.poster.avif?t=1761218317\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/f2210fce606d833c207fcf60055b9233.webm?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/f2210fce606d833c207fcf60055b9233.mp4?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不断扩充你的动物园</strong></h2>经营业务的同时也要不断地发展壮大。那样将会有更多的游客来访，因为会更多的景点让他们在游玩的时间里感到更加愉悦。注意设置一定数量的公共厕所及卫生设施，摆满长椅的休息区和他们能够进餐的地方！还有，别忘了不定时地引进一些有意思的新的动物品种。这是非常重要的环节，游客们不但对动物园流连忘返，而且还会多邀请他们的朋友一起来。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/a3018a4aa654553af10356c3fed3cf51.poster.avif?t=1761218317\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/a3018a4aa654553af10356c3fed3cf51.webm?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129220/extras/a3018a4aa654553af10356c3fed3cf51.mp4?t=1761218317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
